  "title": "Senior Solution Architect (Cloud)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🔹 Role: Senior Solution Architect (Cloud)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>As a Senior Solution Architect, you will lead the design of <strong>scalable, secure, and high-performance cloud architectures</strong>for enterprise and public sector engagements. You will drive technical strategy, mentor teams, and deliver complex solutions leveraging <strong>AWS, Kubernetes, HashiCorp tools, and DevOps/DevSecOps practices</strong>.</p><p><strong>🔹 Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>• Design and implement end-to-end <strong>AWS architectures</strong> ensuring high availability, security, and cost optimization<br />• Architect solutions using <strong>AWS networking, security, serverless (Lambda, API Gateway)</strong> and data services (S3, Glue, Athena, EMR, Redshift)<br />• Lead <strong>Kubernetes (EKS)</strong> based microservices architectures and hybrid/multi-cloud strategies<br />• Implement and manage <strong>HashiCorp Terraform Enterprise (TFE)</strong> and <strong>Vault HA clusters</strong><br />• Drive <strong>DevOps/DevSecOps</strong> pipelines (CI/CD, GitOps, automation, security scans)<br />• Translate business requirements into technical roadmaps and migration strategies<br />• Mentor junior architects and present solutions to senior stakeholders and executives</p><p><strong>🔹 Required Skills & Experience</strong></p><p>• <strong>7+ years</strong> of experience in Cloud Architecture with deep <strong>AWS expertise</strong><br />• Strong hands-on experience in <strong>VPC, Direct Connect, serverless architectures & data pipelines</strong><br />• Expertise in <strong>HashiCorp Terraform Enterprise & Vault (HA / PKI / Secrets)</strong><br />• Solid experience with <strong>Kubernetes (EKS/GKE), Docker, Helm</strong><br />• DevOps/DevSecOps exposure: <strong>Terraform, CloudFormation, GitOps, CI/CD, Python/Bash</strong><br />• Strong communication and stakeholder management skills</p><p><strong>🔹 Preferred Certifications</strong></p><p>• AWS Solution Architect – <strong>Professional</strong><br />• AWS Security Specialty<br />• AWS Advanced Networking Specialty<br />• HashiCorp Terraform & Vault Certifications<br />• CKA / CKAD</p>",
